snippet.title: Night Raid (Dos game 1993)
snippet.description:
Night Raid is a defense (defence) shooter game.
It's similar with a classic game called Paratrooper of Orion Software released in 1982.
The aim of the game is that you ought to kill off parachutists who parachute from a airplane.
